        <h4 class="roboto-condensed">Arjun M.</h4>
        <p>★★★★☆</p>
        <p>"Loved the material quality. Fast delivery."</p>
      </div>
      <div class="review-card">
        <h4 class="roboto-condensed">Megha K.</h4>
        <p>★★★★★</p>
        <p>"Stylish and durable. Totally worth it!"</p>
      </div>
      <div class="review-card">
